    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so with the arm, how do i actually know when the rate is gonna jump? like is there a cap or something that keeps it from going crazy? just trying to figure out if the lower starting rate is actually worth the risk if it spikes.",
      "source": "evaluator"
